00:06:45.086 --> 00:06:47.046
When can you go back?

00:06:47.046 --> 00:06:51.316
&gt;&gt; Forty-eight hours without any
symptoms or a note from the doc

00:06:51.316 --> 00:06:54.896
that I'm free of a
norovirus infection.

